divs: Sighting Details 1 East bound Buss from SanMarcos Texas to Houston Texas2 Northern Horizon lit up like a City, as 20 Lights in V formation flew over3 Looked like aircraft, but as they aproached, we saw it wasnt ours.4 Extreme excitement and concern for all of usthey continued over us to the south and a split second later, everyone wastotally quiet and stareing strait ahead, as tho they seen nothing.5 20 bright lights in V formation went from N.horizon to S. horizon in less than30 seconds, in a strait path directly over the buss at high altitude.6 The Lights continued south over the flat plains, and disapeared over thehorizon.
trends: There have been 188 other sightings in Austin

Summary: 20 Bright Lights in V formation very high fast
